import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { ChevronDown, ChevronRight, Play, CheckCircle, XCircle, Clock } from 'lucide-react'; const ExecutionDetails: React.FC = () => { const [expandedNodes, setExpandedNodes] = useState([]); // 节点执行数据 const nodeExecutionData = [ { nodeId: 'start-1', nodeName: '开始节点', nodeType: 'start', status: 'completed', startTime: '2024-08-19 14:50:00', endTime: '2024-08-19 14:50:01', duration: '1s', details: '工作流启动成功', inputCount: 0, outputCount: 100, statusColor: 'text-green-600', statusIcon: CheckCircle }, { nodeId: 'parse-1', nodeName: '解析节点-1', nodeType: 'parse', status: 'completed', startTime: '2024-08-19 14:50:01', endTime: '2024-08-19 14:51:30', duration: '1分29秒', details: '解析了50个文件，成功48个', inputCount: 50, outputCount: 48, statusColor: 'text-green-600', statusIcon: CheckCircle }, { nodeId: 'parse-2', nodeName: '解析节点-2', nodeType: 'parse', status: 'completed', startTime: '2024-08-19 14:50:01', endTime: '2024-08-19 14:51:45', duration: '1分44秒', details: '解析了50个文件，成功47个', inputCount: 50, outputCount: 47, statusColor: 'text-green-600', statusIcon: CheckCircle }, { nodeId: 'clean-1', nodeName: '清洗节点', nodeType: 'clean', status: 'running', startTime: '2024-08-19 14:51:45', endTime: '-', duration: '进行中', details: '正在清洗数据，已处理70/95', inputCount: 95, outputCount: 70, statusColor: 'text-blue-600', statusIcon: Play }, { nodeId: 'enhance-1', nodeName: '增强节点', nodeType: 'enhance', status: 'pending', startTime: '-', endTime: '-', duration: '-', details: '等待上一节点完成', inputCount: 0, outputCount: 0, statusColor: 'text-gray-600', statusIcon: Clock }, { nodeId: 'end-1', nodeName: '结束节点', nodeType: 'end', status: 'pending', startTime: '-', endTime: '-', duration: '-', details: '等待所有节点完成', inputCount: 0, outputCount: 0, statusColor: 'text-gray-600', statusIcon: Clock } ]; // 文件级别执行数据 const tableData = [ { fileName: '通过评分网', status: '处理完成', fileType: 'jpg', createTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', updateTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', note: '-', statusColor: 'text-green-600', statusIcon: '●' }, { fileName: '通过评分网', status: '处理失败', fileType: 'jpg', createTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', updateTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', note: '-', statusColor: 'text-red-600', statusIcon: '●' }, { fileName: '通过评分网', status: '处理失败', fileType: 'jpg', createTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', updateTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', note: '文件上传2G,超过48.8 TB', statusColor: 'text-red-600', statusIcon: '●' }, { fileName: '通过评分网', status: '处理完成', fileType: 'docx', createTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', updateTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', note: '-', statusColor: 'text-green-600', statusIcon: '●' }, { fileName: '通过评分网', status: '处理完成', fileType: 'docx', createTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', updateTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', note: '-', statusColor: 'text-green-600', statusIcon: '●' }, { fileName: '通过评分网', status: '处理失败', fileType: 'docx', createTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', updateTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', note: '文件上传错误', statusColor: 'text-red-600', statusIcon: '●' }, { fileName: '通过评分网', status: '等待中', fileType: 'txt', createTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', updateTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', note: '-', statusColor: 'text-gray-600', statusIcon: '○' }, { fileName: '通过评分网', status: '等待中', fileType: 'txt', createTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', updateTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', note: '-', statusColor: 'text-gray-600', statusIcon: '○' }, { fileName: '通过评分网', status: '处理完成', fileType: 'txt', createTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', updateTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', note: '-', statusColor: 'text-green-600', statusIcon: '●' }, { fileName: '通过评分网', status: '处理完成', fileType: 'txt', createTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', updateTime: '2024-08-19 14:52:24', note: '-', statusColor: 'text-green-600', statusIcon: '●' } ]; const toggleNodeExpansion = (nodeId: string) => { setExpandedNodes(prev => prev.includes(nodeId) ? prev.filter(id => id !== nodeId) : [...prev, nodeId] ); }; const getNodeTypeColor = (nodeType: string) => { switch (nodeType) { case 'start': return 'bg-green-50 border-green-200'; case 'parse': return 'bg-blue-50 border-blue-200'; case 'clean': return 'bg-purple-50 border-purple-200'; case 'enhance': return 'bg-orange-50 border-orange-200'; case 'end': return 'bg-gray-50 border-gray-200'; default: return 'bg-gray-50 border-gray-200'; } }; return (

执行详情

{/* 节点执行详情 */}

节点执行状态

{nodeExecutionData.map((node) => { const isExpanded = expandedNodes.includes(node.nodeId); const IconComponent = node.statusIcon; return (
toggleNodeExpansion(node.nodeId)} >

{node.nodeName}

{node.details}

输入: {node.inputCount} | 输出: {node.outputCount}
耗时: {node.duration}
{isExpanded ? ( ) : ( )}

开始时间: {node.startTime}
结束时间: {node.endTime}
节点ID: {node.nodeId}
状态: {node.status === 'completed' ? '已完成' : node.status === 'running' ? '运行中' : '等待中'}
)}
); })}
{/* 分隔线 */}
{/* 文件处理详情 */}

文件处理详情

文件处理进度量 处理成功 48/100 处理失败数 5/100

文件名 状态 文件类型 开始时间 结束时间 详情
{row.fileName} {row.statusIcon} {row.status} {row.fileType} {row.createTime} {row.updateTime} {row.note}

); }; export default ExecutionDetails;
